text: Phacellus plurimaculatus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Galileo and Martins in 2001. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Phacellus plurimaculatus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 2001
